# Changelog

## [0.3.0] - 2022-01-16

### Changed
- rework all functions for speed-values to use unsigned-int values instead of signed-int


## [0.2.0] - 2021-11-19

### Added
- check if hyperthreading is supported and enabled
- swtich to enable/disable hyperthreading
- function to get core-id of a thread
- check if raple is active
- more error-messages and some missing validations

### Changed
- use error-container of libKitsunemimiCommon for error-output
- change J to Ws in Rapl-output
- rename socket to package


## [0.1.1] - 2021-10-27

### Changed
- update requirements


## [0.1.0] - 2021-10-24

### Added
- read number of cpu-threads
- read number of cpu-sockets
- check which cpu-thread is on which socket
- check which cpu-threads sharing the same physical core
- read cpu-speed
- change minimum and maximum cpu-speed
- read energy-consumption of cpu
- read total amount of local memory
- read free amount of local memory
